data.title: Migrasi FTTH Pending Brim
data.meta_description: Migrasi FTTH Pending Brim - Free ebook download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls / .xlsx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. The document contains a list of fiber nodes, their descriptions, and scheduling information. It includes fiber nodes from various areas in Jakarta identified by their codes. The scheduling column indicates target dates for email blasts related to the different nodes ranging from November 5th to 27th 2022.
